704125f-a.title: Brooklyn: Emmons Avenue - Nostrand Avenue
704125f-a.text:
Emmons Ave., at the N.E. corner of Nostrand Ave. The view shows a
drive-way to a Carriage Shed, one of the few remaining in SBeepshead Bay.
July 13, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPPODUCTIONS.
